{"tid":872115,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊黎睇下共朝皇帝「謚號」同訃告規格分別","createTime":"2018-10-22T12:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T13:32:05.000Z","uid":38255,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"552f488ee49349de111d669527e693cf59e3fe7a","tid":872115,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"以前皇帝皇后除左三四隻字既廟號，仲有謚號，例如<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">武則天既「則天順聖皇后」\n唐玄宗既「至道大聖大明孝皇帝」</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n之後越黎越長變水蛇春級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">宋太祖既「啟運立極英武睿文神德聖功至明大孝皇帝」\n朱元璋既「開天行道肇紀立極大聖至神仁文義武俊德成功高皇帝」\n明成祖既「啟天弘道高明肇運聖武神功純仁至孝文皇帝」\n乾隆既「法天隆運至誠先覺體元立極敷文奮武欽明孝慈神聖純皇帝」\n慈禧既「孝欽慈禧端佑康頤昭豫莊誠壽恭欽獻崇熙配天興聖顯皇后」</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n其實共匪都有個類似既劣化版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">毛澤東官方評價為「偉大的馬克思主義者，偉大的無產階級革命家、戰略家、理論家，馬克思主義中國化的偉大開拓者，近代以來中國偉大的愛國者和民族英雄，中國共產黨第一代中央領導集體的核心」\n\n周恩來官方評價為「偉大的馬克思主義者，偉大的無產階級革命家、政治家、軍事家、外交家，黨和國家主要領導人之一」\n\n鄧小平官方評價為「偉大的馬克思主義者，偉大的無產階級革命家、政治家、軍事家、外交家，中國共產黨第二代中央領導集體的核心」\n\n胡耀邦官方評價為「久經考驗的忠誠的共產主義戰士，偉大的無產階級革命家、政治家，我軍傑出的政治工作者，長期擔任黨的重要領導職務的卓越領導人。」</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n然後仲有人民日報訃告規格既分別，誰大誰細相當一目了然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（如果古代有報紙都應該咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/203843_43d0aacaa76dae0a0d7abff833051185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F203843_43d0aacaa76dae0a0d7abff833051185.jpg&h=ee55c602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/203841_e2c8dc8e6cdefdef4ac3ae54dbfd0b9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F203841_e2c8dc8e6cdefdef4ac3ae54dbfd0b9d.jpg&h=b3385038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/203834_a7aa39ab54a58e772b7e5ce1f5ae3bf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F203834_a7aa39ab54a58e772b7e5ce1f5ae3bf8.jpg&h=d8161137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/204236_1dfc2ea1ff21e055050cb430c8b4aead.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F204236_1dfc2ea1ff21e055050cb430c8b4aead.jpg&h=618cc394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/203826_7a7f2c748d997e33f6fe8d9779cb3295.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F203826_7a7f2c748d997e33f6fe8d9779cb3295.jpg&h=d02a421e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知將來江澤民、胡溫、習近平、李克強死左會分別係邊隻規格呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 假設佢地死果陣共朝未亡的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1c599cfd85ce323cdf6e07b856fe4670658022","tid":872115,"uid":38255,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T13:26:50.000Z","msg":"再補三個規格更水皮既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近代中共重要外交人物錢其琛<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/211914_eb3feeb8fb50165cb1be3b18f0de48d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F211914_eb3feeb8fb50165cb1be3b18f0de48d5.jpg&h=5c05b24a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔同之前既例子咁擺係左上角，擺係右下角就廢得多，但呢個例子d字尚算工整顯眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n權鬥失敗者既共惠帝華國峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/211912_374952ed94faead6bd1f58901573044d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F211912_374952ed94faead6bd1f58901573044d.jpg&h=940b5515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同樣右下角但個格更細d字更唔顯眼<br />\n<br />\n六四事件後被打落台既趙紫陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/211910_0d2254a34887f0a830cf83bb96062760.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F211910_0d2254a34887f0a830cf83bb96062760.jpg&h=d5be56d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連相都無又求其攝係一角<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過有更廢既連頭版都入唔到就唔搵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31f58b6c2189aeeaa2b82cdff779baee2cd2972","tid":872115,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T13:32:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再補三個規格更水皮既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近代中共重要外交人物錢其琛<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/211914_eb3feeb8fb50165cb1be3b18f0de48d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F211914_eb3feeb8fb50165cb1be3b18f0de48d5.jpg&h=5c05b24a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔同之前既例子咁擺係左上角，擺係右下角就廢得多，但呢個例子d字尚算工整顯眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n權鬥失敗者既共惠帝華國峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/211912_374952ed94faead6bd1f58901573044d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F211912_374952ed94faead6bd1f58901573044d.jpg&h=940b5515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同樣右下角但個格更細d字更唔顯眼<br />\n<br />\n六四事件後被打落台既趙紫陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/211910_